04ab80cf-6891-45db-b604-1f8506adef43	965e1498-599b-4744-9b09-410f6c6da286	af4066ab-2bc3-46bc-88be-81deaa798ccb	completed	193	2026-06-12 17:46:44.088+08	2026-06-12 17:47:14.023+08	2026-06-12 17:46:44.08865+08	\N	[{"type": "writing", "feedback": {"message": "作文评分完成"}, "max_score": 106.5, "section_id": "mqaib3crmo49af", "total_score": 94, "section_title": "Writing", "question_results": [{"score": 94, "feedback": "你写的这篇短文非常棒！开头准确引用了给定的句子，结构也特别清晰——先讲专业知识，再讲实践能力和心理素质，最后用自己的亲身经历来佐证，逻辑层层递进，让人读起来很顺畅。你能把“积极面对挑战”这样一个大主题落到实处，提到实习、校园活动和抗压心态，说明你真的在思考大学生怎样才能准备好迎接挑战。特别是你那段个人经历，从缺乏自信到通过学习和挑战变得更强，既真实又有感染力，让文章一下子有了温度。语言表达也基本准确，有些小地方如“keeps moving forward”可以更自然地说成“keep moving forward”，但整体不影响理解。你做到了学以致用，很棒！继续保持这样的思考深度和表达热情，下一篇可以再尝试多些过渡词，比如“firstly”“moreover”，让段落衔接更紧密。你已经走在正确的路上了，加油！", "max_score": 106.5, "is_correct": false, "user_answer": "# Be Ready for Challenges\\nLiving in an increasingly competitive world, college students should better prepare themselves to confront various challenges.\\n\\nTo start with, we must master professional knowledge, which lays a solid foundation for future development. Meanwhile, it is necessary to develop practical abilities. Taking part in internships and campus activities helps us gain real-world experience and teamwork skills. Apart from capabilities, a strong mental state is also essential. Competition always brings pressure and failures, so we need to learn to stay calm and keep moving forward.\\n\\nFrom my own experience, I used to lack confidence when facing tough tasks. By keeping learning and challenging myself, I have become more capable and resilient.\\n\\nIn short, well-rounded preparation equips us to deal with all difficulties. Only in this way can we stand firm in fierce competition and achieve our goals.\\n(Word count: 168)", "correct_answer": "这里填参考答案：\\n这是参考答案", "sub_question_id": "mqaib3crr3wnrp"}]}, {"type": "listening", "feedback": null, "max_score": 28.4, "section_id": "mqaih3548we9w3", "total_score": 0, "section_title": "Section