, "max_score": 14.2, "is_correct": false, "user_answer": "", "correct_answer": "A", "sub_question_id": "mqannc7rxqedqs"}]}, {"type": "reading_careful", "feedback": null, "max_score": 71, "section_id": "mqant730sfnmty", "total_score": 0, "section_title": "Section C", "question_results": [{"score": 0, "max_score": 14.2, "is_correct": false, "user_answer": "", "correct_answer": "A", "sub_question_id": "mqant730mvj5mz"}, {"score": 0, "max_score": 14.2, "is_correct": false, "user_answer": "", "correct_answer": "A", "sub_question_id": "mqanum40zb3jts"}, {"score": 0, "max_score": 14.2, "is_correct": false, "user_answer": "", "correct_answer": "A", "sub_question_id": "mqanut3o2bjgk1"}, {"score": 0, "max_score": 14.2, "is_correct": false, "user_answer": "", "correct_answer": "A", "sub_question_id": "mqanutfx70pkbj"}, {"score": 0, "max_score": 14.2, "is_correct": false, "user_answer": "", "correct_answer": "A", "sub_question_id": "mqanutp75z1gxq"}]}, {"type": "translation", "feedback": {"message": "翻译评分完成"}, "max_score": 106.5, "section_id": "mqanvm8gsuosnq", "total_score": 99, "section_title": "Translation", "question_results": [{"score": 99, "feedback": "你这次的翻译完成得非常出色！整篇译文用词准确、句式流畅，几乎完美再现了原文的思想内涵。像'deeply rooted in Chinese people's minds and behaviors'、'a widely observed code of conduct'这些表达，既符合英语习惯，又保留了中文的韵味。你对长难句的处理也很自然，比如'has become a social consensus'后面接具体例子的衔接很顺畅。读完全文，感觉你对尊老美德的理解很深刻，并且能用地道的英语把它讲给世界听。如果非要说一点小建议，那就是个别词语可以更简洁，比如'rolled out a host of policies'换成'introduced various policies'也许更口语化一些；另外段落之间的过渡可以再自然一点点，比如加个'As a result'之类的连接词。不过这些都是锦上添花的小细节啦！整体来说，你已经达到了很高的翻译水平，继续加油，未来可期！", "max_score": 106.5, "is_correct": false, "user_answer": "Respecting the elderly is a traditional virtue of the Chinese nation. It is deeply rooted in Chinese people's minds and behaviors, and has become a widely observed code of conduct and social norm. This virtue has been well passed down across modern China.\\nAll sectors of society strive to foster a caring atmosphere for the elderly. Offering convenient services to seniors has become a social consensus. For instance, communities have set up special canteens for the elderly, and priority seats are arranged in public places. The government has also rolled out a host of policies to fully safeguard the rights and interests of senior citizens.\\nRespecting the elderly serves as an important cornerstone for social harmony and development. It helps nurture a sound social environment and boosts the progress of social civilization.", "correct_answer": "这里填参考答案：\\n这是参考答案", "sub_question_id": "mqanvm8gvpzgiv"}]}]	710
